{"tid":2452654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"智利3分1人接種科興疫苗 確診不跌反升增30%","createTime":"2021-03-19T03:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T03:51:36.000Z","uid":254371,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b13c625df09a4c2dff702748bba204681a58eaee","tid":2452654,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情持續，多國也陸續展開疫苗接種。位於南美洲的智利與香港同樣，也是選用中國科興疫苗，智利當地已有3分1人接種首針科興疫苗，但確診卻不跌反升，過去7日平均每日新增超過5,000宗確診。<br />\n<br />\n據疫苗數據網站 Our World In Data 顯示，智利自2月初起大規模接種科興疫苗，首兩針接種率分別急升至逾25%和10%，當中有逾90%人都是打科興。但同一時間，當地每日確診數字竟不跌反升，由2月初約4,000宗升至近期約5,000宗，升幅近30%。<br />\n當地深切治療部醫生表示，即使重症病房在上星期增加一倍，但病床使用率仍然爆滿，其中不少70歲以上長者接種了科興疫苗最終仍病逝，近日也出現較多年輕重症患者。"},{"pid":"5fa1f08b1ec327a420cad3c18d16d79fe135c0cf","tid":2452654,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"支那狗都唔撚打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfdd0a78625fd3ae1a527339ac263b9259a4bd4","tid":2452654,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"3分1人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5aca6111fe0349b64a621731f2ec0d618b0073","tid":2452654,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"智利武漢肺炎病人已犯國安法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc9c07088a7161a49c70aead7101f8a72730e75","tid":2452654,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"其實智利先係科與疫苗研發地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最大型測試活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d1c06dd2fd11da260c87696a86ee6dddef14b3","tid":2452654,"uid":212144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"